                        text="&lt;p>With 48 countries and nearly 2,300 languages, Asia is defined by a wide spectrum of customs, religious beliefs and cultures. The Asian Leadership Network fosters belonging and inclusion and fosters a workplace where every voice is heard and valued.&lt;/p>&lt;p>The Asian Leadership Network fosters a diverse and inclusive environment where every voice is heard and valued. ALN promotes a sense of belonging and community by enabling all employees to reach their full potential. We do this through:&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;ul> &lt;li>Raising awareness about cultural diversity&lt;/li> &lt;li>Informal mentoring and networking&lt;/li> &lt;li>Business and patient impact&lt;/li> &lt;/ul>&lt;/p>"/>
